{"tid":885101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤貨尾】海翩滙複式戶標售4,664萬 呎價2.35萬創新高","createTime":"2018-11-01T05:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T06:54:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"34d1dfc084a37c163ac355f55d9a6c78acacbb7e","tid":885101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181031/large/1540990961_ef61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181031%2Flarge%2F1540990961_ef61.jpg&h=fba58365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華懋近期推售元朗新盤朗城滙，另一邊同步以招標形式推售旗下兩個新盤的貨尾單位。一手成交紀錄冊顯示，其中已屆現樓的將軍澳海翩滙今日售出1座11及12樓G室頂層複式單位，實用面積1,985方呎，連563方呎天台，成交價4,664.8萬元，呎價2.35萬元，創項目新高。<br />\n<br />\n對上紀錄於2016年12月所造，為2座11及12樓F室，實用面積1,992方呎，連574方呎的天台，成交價4,196萬元，實用呎價21,065元，是次再推高11.5%。項目尚餘1伙複式戶待售，為1座11樓至12樓F室，實用面積2,277方呎，天台689方呎。<br />\n<br />\n另外，同系的大埔富．盈門今日亦錄成交，單位為2座18及19樓A室頂層複式戶，實用面積1,574方呎，連64方平台及272方呎天台，並附一個車位，以2,698.4萬元成交，呎價17,144元。"},{"pid":"7e419ed6ccb2f948abb22ddbc1fbf79f125b949d","tid":885101,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"903be1c18fcffda967a78663ac6772fea16ba9ea","tid":885101,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"太遠唔計"},{"pid":"10e7a800b22d0cb6f3c091c468eef669e6fb452a","tid":885101,"uid":218477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"唔怕水浸咩"},{"pid":"6f624ca026ef4ec576f29da11ec1e715916ddeb6","tid":885101,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e419ed6ccb2f948abb22ddbc1fbf79f125b949d","tid":885101,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"4000萬移民住土皇帝都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"